This Play application shows how to 
=====================================

Sample application from CHAPTER 8 of book 'Building a single-page JavaScript application with JSON'

This is a single page Play application featuring :

1. Defining RESTful webservice
2. Sending JSON to web browser 
3. Parsing JSON from HTTP request
4. Converting between JSON data  and SCALA objects
5. VAlidating JSON Data 
6. Authenticating JSON web service requests

To Check the JSON :
$ curl --include http://localhost:9000/products
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: 71
[5010255079763,5018206244611,5018206244666,5018306312913,5018306332812]
